    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数学大师是一款受复古游戏启发的小型教育数学游戏。练习基本数学，同时改进计算器。在每次训练中不断进步，获得所有成就，并向其他玩家展示您值得跻身排行榜前列。<strong>走上数学大师之路</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/01d09be6ed821d9e27c8da4f4b7b82be.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >屏幕上方会生成带有操作的方块供玩家解决。在游戏过程中，这些方块会掉落。如果你积累的方块超出了允许的范围，或者犯了超出允许的错误，那么游戏就会结束。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/22d0578322a3062de803dc01248c7a0e.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有操作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仅求和运算。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仅做减法运算。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仅限乘法运算。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只做除法运算。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/2accd09f38232d927e72d9e7e25fb2d6.poster.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/2accd09f38232d927e72d9e7e25fb2d6.webm?t=1735908816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>实现所有目标</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得全部 <strong>40</strong> 项成就和全部 <strong>28</strong> 个可用贴纸。利用这一点，在墙上贴一些贴纸。 ♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/5de59b143b55b18b485d4f84ca1e5caf.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在线排行榜：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有超过 5 个在线排行榜可供使用。发展你的数学推理能力并达到跻身最佳之列所需的分数。让所有数学玩家都能在桌子上看到您的名字。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/3eda15c8847e87900e13d80d566bb787.poster.avif?t=1735908816\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/3eda15c8847e87900e13d80d566bb787.webm?t=1735908816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/3eda15c8847e87900e13d80d566bb787.mp4?t=1735908816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战本地其他玩家：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设立一个锦标赛，在本地与您的朋友和家人比赛。锦标赛以比赛形式进行。在每一轮比赛中，每位选手都有权在比赛中展示自己的技能。</p>",
